data.name: ERROR_TypeAlreadyPatchedByNGO
data.value: Plugin {0} is trying to patch type {1} via attribute but the type is suspected to be patched by NGO IL Post-Processor. Stopping patch for type; If you suspect this is incorrect, try removing any methods named `InitializeRPCS_{1}` from your type OR remove the [PatchNetworkBehaviour] to disable Runtime Patching.
